{
  "stem": "4686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there they put up-- put us up into houses, organized, dressed, fed to bring us back to the normal-- normal living of life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what was that like?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was that your first experience of a kind-- of a normal way of life in about a year?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war, definitely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was good time, interesting time, these places were run by the different Zionist groups.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were people who knew how to work with children to make their life interesting and to teach them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is we first started to learn about Zionism and Israel and give us a-- a-- a brighter future.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is where we also heard and started to learn about what did really happen and heard about Auschwitz and Dachau and Bergen-Belsen and et cetera.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was difficult to hear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to see the-- these-- these films were mostly American and Russian films, what they found.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But also a very large number of films, what the Germans made themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's got into the hands of the Russian and English and American military.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And out of that document, films were made.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on when school started up, these films were very widely shown in all schools-- all schools-- to all school children in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the concentration camps, on ghettos, on-- on-- on Poland, in Babi Yar, and-- and all these things what the Germans filmed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it got into these news films, so-called news films.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the schools, it was an organized thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a very strong feeling about it what the Germans did to the people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Naturally.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
